<!-- templates/about_content.xml -->
<odoo>
    <template id="s_eventzo_about_content" name="Eventzo About Content">
        <section class="s_eventzo_about_content pt96 pb96" data-name="Eventzo About Content">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <!-- Logo Section -->
                    <div class="col-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        <div class="eventzo_about_logo_wrapper">
                            <div class="eventzo_about_logo_circle">
                                <img src="/theme_eventzo/static/src/img/header.png" alt="Eventzo Logo"
                                     class="eventzo_about_logo"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="eventzo_about_logo_decoration"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Content Section -->
                    <div class="col-lg-7">
                        <div class="eventzo_about_text_content">
                            <h2 class="eventzo_about_section_title">Who We Are</h2>
                            <div class="eventzo_about_divider">
                                <span class="eventzo_divider_line"></span>
                                <span class="eventzo_divider_dot"></span>
                            </div>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                <strong>Eventzo Event Management</strong>
                                is World's premier ISO 9001:2015 certified event management company, dedicated to
                                transforming your vision into unforgettable experiences. With over 15 years of
                                excellence in the industry, we have successfully orchestrated more than 1,700 events
                                across the beautiful world.
                            </p>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                Our journey began with a simple yet powerful mission: to create extraordinary moments
                                that last a lifetime. From intimate gatherings to grand celebrations, from corporate
                                conferences to dream destination weddings, we bring unparalleled expertise, creativity,
                                and attention to detail to every project we undertake.
                            </p>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                What sets us apart is our comprehensive approach to event management. We don't just plan
                                events; we craft experiences. Our dedicated team of seasoned professionals works
                                tirelessly to understand your unique requirements, preferences, and aspirations. Whether
                                you're envisioning a beachside wedding in Goa's pristine coastline, a sophisticated
                                corporate event, a vibrant cultural celebration, or an elegant reception, we have the
                                expertise and resources to bring your dreams to life.
                            </p>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                We pride ourselves on offering end-to-end event management solutions that cover every
                                aspect of your celebration. From venue selection and booking assistance to décor design,
                                entertainment coordination, catering management, and technical support – we handle it
                                all. Our extensive network of trusted vendors and venues ensures that you
                                have access to the finest resources for your event.
                            </p>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                Our commitment to excellence has earned us the trust of clients not only from across
                                India but also from around the world. We understand the cultural nuances, local
                                traditions, and contemporary trends that make events truly special. This unique
                                blend of traditional values and modern innovation allows us to create celebrations that
                                are both authentic and contemporary.
                            </p>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                At Eventzo, we believe that every event tells a story – your story. Our mission is to
                                ensure that every chapter of your celebration is written with precision, creativity, and
                                care. With a customer rating of 4.8 out of 5 and over 1,500 satisfied clients, we
                                continue to set the standard for event management excellence.
                            </p>

                            <p class="eventzo_about_paragraph">
                                Let us be your partner in creating memories that will be cherished for generations.
                                Whether you're planning a wedding, corporate event, private party, or any special
                                occasion, Eventzo Event Management is here to make it extraordinary.
                            </p>

                            <!-- Key Highlights -->
                            <div class="eventzo_about_highlights">
                                <div class="row g-3 mt-4">
                                    <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                        <div class="eventzo_highlight_item">
                                            <i class="fa fa-certificate"></i>
                                            <span>ISO Certified</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                        <div class="eventzo_highlight_item">
                                            <i class="fa fa-shield"></i>
                                            <span>15+ Years</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                        <div class="eventzo_highlight_item">
                                            <i class="fa fa-users"></i>
                                            <span>1500+ Clients</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                        <div class="eventzo_highlight_item">
                                            <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                                            <span>4.8 Rating</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
                <div class="row mt-5 pt-5">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="eventzo_why_choose_wrapper">
                            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                                <h2 class="eventzo_why_choose_title">Why Choose Eventzo?</h2>
                                <div class="eventzo_about_divider justify-content-center">
                                    <span class="eventzo_divider_line"></span>
                                    <span class="eventzo_divider_dot"></span>
                                    <span class="eventzo_divider_line"></span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="eventzo_why_choose_subtitle">Discover what makes us Wolrd's most trusted
                                    event management partner
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row g-4">
                                <!-- Reason 1 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="eventzo_reason_card">
                                        <div class="eventzo_reason_icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">ISO 9001:2015 Certified</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            We are proud to be an ISO certified event management company, ensuring
                                            international quality standards in every aspect of our service delivery.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Reason 2 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
