                                            <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">Personalized Approach</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            We understand that every event is unique. Our team works closely with you to
                                            understand your vision and create experiences tailored to your needs.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Reason 5 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="eventzo_reason_card">
                                        <div class="eventzo_reason_icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-chain"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">Extensive Network</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            Our strong relationships with premier venues, vendors, and service providers
