                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Reason 6 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="eventzo_reason_card">
                                        <div class="eventzo_reason_icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-smile-o"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">1500+ Happy Clients</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            With over 1,500 satisfied clients and a 4.8-star rating, our track record
                                            speaks for itself. Join our family of delighted customers today.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Reason 7 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="eventzo_reason_card">
                                        <div class="eventzo_reason_icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">Wide Expertise</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            As a premier event company, we have deep local knowledge and cultural
                                            understanding to create authentic, memorable celebrations.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Reason 8 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="eventzo_reason_card">
                                        <div class="eventzo_reason_icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-superpowers"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">Creative Innovation</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            Our creative team brings fresh ideas and innovative concepts to make your
                                            event stand out, blending tradition with modern trends perfectly.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Reason 9 -->
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="eventzo_reason_card">
                                        <div class="eventzo_reason_icon">
                                            <i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h3 class="eventzo_reason_title">Timely Execution</h3>
                                        <p class="eventzo_reason_text">
                                            We value your time and ensure meticulous planning and flawless execution,
                                            delivering your event on schedule without compromising on quality.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </template>
</odoo>